reviewText: Not bad.  Get "Way of Life" first.

I own quite a few ski movies, Tangerine Dream, Cordoroy, Long Story Short, Show and Prove, Teddy Bear Crisis, Higher Ground....etc  This is by far my favorite with Cordoroy second.  TGR always seems to put out great movies.  I love big mountain skiing and this movie is 90% big mountain.  Music is good as well
